          <outline text="理性情绪行为疗法 REBT Rational-Emotive Behavior Therapy 识别并重构非理性信念，是 CBT 的前身" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22bold%20text-color-red%22%3E%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22bold%22%3E%E7%96%97%E6%B3%95%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22bold%20text-color-red%22%3EREBT%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22text-color-red%22%3E%20%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22bold%20text-color-yellow%22%3ERational-Emotive%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22bold%22%3EBehavior%20Therapy%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22text-color-blue%22%3E%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%3E%E5%B9%B6%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22text-color-blue%22%3E%E9%87%8D%E6%9E%84%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22text-color-yellow%22%3E%E9%9D%9E%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%B5%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22text-color-green%22%3E%E6%98%AF%20CBT%20%E7%9A%84%E5%89%8D%E8%BA%AB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="辩证行为疗法 DBT Dialectical Behavior Therapy 接纳自我的同时改变不健康行为模式" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%20class=%22bold%20text-color-red%22%3E%E8%BE%A9%E8%AF%81%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22bold%22%3E%E7%96%97%E6%B3%95%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22bold%20text-color-red%22%3EDBT%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22text-color-red%22%3E%20%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22bold%20text-color-yellow%22%3EDialectical%20Behavior%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22bold%22%3ETherapy%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22text-color-blue%22%3E%E6%8E%A5%E7%BA%B3%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22text-color-yellow%22%3E%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%3E%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22text-color-blue%22%3E%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22text-color-yellow%22%3E%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
            <outline text="核心技能：情绪调节、痛苦忍受、人际效能、正念" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22text-color-green%22%3E%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E8%B0%83%E8%8A%82%E3%80%81%E7%97%9B%E8%8B%A6%E5%BF%8D%E5%8F%97%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%85%E6%95%88%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E6%AD%A3%E5%BF%B5%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
